<v-form v-model="valid">
    <v-text-field
        v-model="nome"
        :rules="nomeRules"
        label="Nome"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
        v-model="anoInicio"
        :rules="anoInicioRules"
        label="Ano de Início"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
        v-model="anoTermino"
        :rules="anoTerminoRules"
        label="Ano de Término"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <v-text-field
        v-model="resumo"
        :rules="resumoRules"
        label="Resumo"
        required
    ></v-text-field>
    <!-- TODO inserir tabela com alunos -->
    <v-btn color="success" @click="salvar()">Salvar </v-btn>
    <v-btn color="error"  @click="fecharDialogo()">Voltar </v-btn>
</v-form>
